Subject: [PATCH] ethosu.hpp: Fix gcc15 build issues

https://gcc.gnu.org/gcc-15/porting_to.html#cxx
Some C++ Standard Library headers are no longer
including other headers that were being used
internally by the library.

Upstream-Status: Pending

Signed-off-by: Markus Niebel <Markus.Niebel@ew.tq-group.com>
---
 driver_library/include/ethosu.hpp | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/driver_library/include/ethosu.hpp b/driver_library/include/ethosu.hpp
index f8f7598..977a716 100644
--- a/driver_library/include/ethosu.hpp
+++ b/driver_library/include/ethosu.hpp
@@ -19,6 +19,7 @@
 #pragma once
 
 #include <algorithm>
+#include <cstdint>
 #include <iostream>
 #include <memory>
 #include <string>
